    <main>
      <div class="page-header">
        <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="games.html">games</a> // halo</p>
        <h1>Halo</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Wars, ODSTs, Spartans. The franchise that defined a console generation and never really let go.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FEATURED: REACH -->
      <div class="featured-banner">
        <div class="feat-cover">
          <img src="images/HaloReachAlexandria.png" alt="Halo Reach" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'"/>
          <div class="feat-cover-placeholder" style="display:none">Halo: Reach</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="feat-label">// editor's pick</p>
          <h2>Halo: Reach</h2>
          <p>Noble Team. Reach falls. You already know the ending — but Bungie makes you feel every step of it. A prequel that hits harder than any finale, Reach is simultaneously a love letter and a eulogy for everything the franchise built. The multiplayer was surgical; the campaign, devastating.</p>
          <p class="feat-rating">★★★★★</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="section-divider">// the collection — chronological order</p>

      <div class="game-grid" id="haloGrid">

        <!-- Halo Wars 2009 -->
        <div class="game-card">
          <div class="game-card-inner">
            <div class="cover-wrap"><div class="cover-placeholder">Halo Wars</div></div>
            <span class="cover-caption">RTS set in the Halo universe</span>
            <p class="game-title">Halo Wars</p>
            <p class="game-year">2009</p>
            <p class="star-rating">★★★☆☆</p>
            <p class="game-blurb">A surprisingly competent RTS on console. Spirit of Fire, Sergeant Forge, and the Flood. Bold experiment that mostly paid off.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ODST 2009 -->
        <div class="game-card">
          <div class="game-card-inner">
            <div class="cover-wrap">
              <img src="images/HaloODST.jpg" alt="Halo 3 ODST" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'"/>
              <div class="cover-placeholder" style="display:none">Halo 3: ODST</div>
            </div>
            <span class="cover-caption">You are not a Spartan. You bleed.</span>
            <p class="game-title">Halo 3: ODST</p>
            <p class="game-year">2009</p>
            <p class="star-rating">★★★★★</p>
            <p class="game-blurb">Rain-soaked New Mombasa at night. Jazz-noir score. Playing as a fragile human in a war between gods — this one hits different every time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Reach 2010 -->
        <div class="game-card">
          <div class="game-card-inner">
            <div class="cover-wrap">
              <img src="images/halo reach.png" alt="Halo Reach" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'"/>
              <div class="cover-placeholder" style="display:none">Halo: Reach</div>
            </div>
            <span class="cover-caption">Noble Six. Last stand on Reach.</span>
            <p class="game-title">Halo: Reach</p>
            <p class="game-year">2010</p>
            <p class="star-rating">★★★★★</p>
            <p class="game-blurb">Bungie's farewell to the franchise. Beautiful, brutal, and bittersweet from start to finish.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Halo 3 -->
        <div class="game-card">
          <div class="game-card-inner">
            <div class="cover-wrap">
              <img src="images/Halo3.jpg" alt="Halo 3" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'"/>
              <div class="cover-placeholder" style="display:none">Halo 3</div>
            </div>
            <span class="cover-caption">Finish the Fight</span>
            <p class="game-title">Halo 3</p>
            <p class="game-year">2007 / MCC</p>
            <p class="star-rating">★★★★★</p>
            <p class="game-blurb">The one that closed the trilogy. Legendary co-op runs, Forge mode, theatre — it invented the social shooter before social shooters were a thing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MCC -->
        <div class="game-card">
          <div class="game-card-inner">
            <div class="cover-wrap"><div class="cover-placeholder">Halo MCC</div></div>
            <span class="cover-caption">The entire Bungie saga, unified</span>
            <p class="game-title">Master Chief Collection</p>
            <p class="game-year">2019 (PC)</p>
            <p class="star-rating">★★★★★</p>
            <p class="game-blurb">Six games, one launcher, cross-play, mod support. The definitive way to experience the Halo saga. A restoration project done right.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Infinite -->
        <div class="game-card">
          <div class="game-card-inner">
            <div class="cover-wrap"><div class="cover-placeholder">Halo Infinite</div></div>
            <span class="cover-caption">Open-world Zeta Halo</span>
            <p class="game-title">Halo Infinite</p>
            <p class="game-year">2021</p>
            <p class="star-rating">★★★★☆</p>
            <p class="game-blurb">The grappleshot changed everything. Open-world campaign, classic multiplayer feel, and a score that could make you cry. Rough launch, brilliant bones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>
